            "a5": "<p>Yes. The built-in RFID blocking lining protects your cards from unauthorized scanning.</p>",
            "q6": "How should I care for my leather?",
            "a6": "<p>Wipe with a soft dry cloth. For deeper care, apply a quality leather conditioner every few months. Avoid prolonged exposure to water or direct sunlight.</p>",
